时空系列在游戏排名和销量上都非常成功。1995年《时空之轮》的超級任天堂版在上市两个月内达到200万套销量，2003年時超任版和PS1版合計已在日本出貨236万套，日本以外出貨29万套<ref name="nppreview2">{{Cite book | year=1995 | author=Averill, Alan | title=Nintendo Power June, 1995 | publisher=Nintendo | page=36}}</ref><ref name="square-sales">{{cite web | date=2003-08-04 | author=Staff | title=Square Enix IR Roadshow Document | url=http://www.square-enix.com/jp/ir/e/explanatory/download/0404-200308040000-01.pdf | publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]] | accessdate=2018-12-12 | format=PDF | archive-date=2006-07-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060723104903/http://www.square-enix.com/jp/ir/e/explanatory/download/0404-200308040000-01.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在1995年末，游戏位列《[[勇者斗恶龙VI_幻之大地|勇者斗恶龙VI 幻之大地]]》和《[[超级大金刚2|超级大金刚2]]》之后，排在当年日本的年度销量榜第三位<ref name="1995 sales">{{cite web |url=http://gameranking.jp/ranking-sale/?0+1995 |title=販売本数ランキング |publisher=ゲームランキング |accessdate=2018-12-12 |archive-date=2012-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120510072555/http://gameranking.jp/ranking-sale/?0+1995 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏在北美发售也相当成功，收录PlayStation重制版的《最终幻想编年史》占据[[NPD集团|NPD]] TRSTS PlayStation销量榜单首位6周<ref name="gamerankings563538"/><ref name="ign-review">{{cite web |date=2001-07-04 |title=IGN: Final Fantasy Chronicles Review |url=http://psx.ign.com/articles/166/166322p1.html |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2006-05-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60eLEcdUY?url=http://psx.ign.com/articles/166/166322p1.html |archivedate=2011-08-03 }}</ref><ref name="FFC-Sales">{{cite web | date=2001-08-15 | last=Wollenschlaeger | first=Alex | title=Final Fantasy Chronicles Tops Sales Charts Six Weeks in a Row | url=http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q3-2001/081501d.html | work=[[RPGamer|RPGamer]] | publisher=Crave Online | accessdate=2009-06-01 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5w3JNIQry?url=http://www.rpgamer.com/news/Q3-2001/081501d.html | archivedate=2011年1月27日 | df= }}</ref>。截至2008年12月，《时空之轮》DS重制版在日本出货49万套，在北美出货22万套<ref name="square-sales-ds">{{cite web |url=http://www.square-enix.com/eng/pdf/news/20090216_01en.pdf#page=19 |title=Results Briefing Session for the Nine-Months Period of the Fiscal Year ending March 31, 2009 |date=2009-02-16 |accessdate=2009-03-01 |publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]] |page=22 |format=PDF |archive-date=2009-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090304001226/http://www.square-enix.com/eng/pdf/news/20090216_01en.pdf#page=19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《穿越时空》亦销量不错，在日本和日本以外分别出货85万套和65万套<ref name="square-sales" />。游戏还作为[[索尼精选辑游戏列表|精选辑]]游戏在美国再发行，并随后再次收录于日本[[Ultimate_Hit|Ultimate Hit]]系列中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://psx.ign.com/articles/097/097578p1.html |title=Chrono Cross Joins Greatest Hits Line |publisher=IGN |date=2001-08-21 |accessdate=2009-06-03 |archive-date=2007-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070604043059/http://psx.ign.com/articles/097/097578p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ultimatehits">{{cite web | date=2006-04-28 | first=Chris | last=Winkler | title=Square Enix Adds 16 to Ultimate Hits Series | url=http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2006/1219.html | publisher=RPGFan | accessdate=2006-07-01 | archive-date=2013-01-21 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6DpkAd7rY?url=http://www.rpgfan.com/news/2006/1219.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2018年，在未含同年首度上市的PC版本下，《超時空之鑰》累計已出貨超過350萬套<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.4gamer.net/games/411/G041119/20180228002/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-11-25 |archive-date=2021-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211124213543/https://www.4gamer.net/games/411/G041119/20180228002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2019年，《超時空之鑰》與《超時空之鑰 次元之旅》两部游戏合計已售出超過550万套<ref name="5.5M"/>。

《时空之轮》六次登上多媒体网站[[IGN|IGN]]“史上100大游戏”榜单的高位——2002年列第4，2005年上半年列第6，2005年下半年列第13，2006年列第2，2007年列第18，2008年列第2<ref name="greatest-games">{{cite web | year=2006 | title=The Top 100 Games Ever | url=http://top100.ign.com/2006/001-010.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2007-08-08 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YQvLgRJE?url=http://top100.ign.com/2006/001-010.html | archivedate=2015年5月11日 | df= }}</ref><ref name="greatest-games2">{{cite web | year=2007 | title=The Top 100 Games Ever | url=http://top100.ign.com/2007/ign_top_game_18.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2008-02-02 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071203032033/http://top100.ign.com/2007/ign_top_game_18.html | archivedate=2007年12月3日 | df= }}</ref><ref name="greatest-games3">{{cite web | year=2008 | title=IGN Top 100 Games 2008 – 2 Chrono Trigger | url=http://top100.ign.com/2008/ign_top_game_2.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2009-03-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090217225935/http://top100.ign.com/2008/ign_top_game_2.html | archive-date=2009-02-17 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]在2006年4月将《时空之轮》列入“史上最伟大游戏”，游戏还在日本杂志《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》举办的“史上最佳100游戏”票选中名列第28<ref name="gamespot-greatestgame">{{cite web |date=2006-04-17 |title=The Greatest Games of All Time |url=http://www.gamespot.com/gamespot/features/all/greatestgames/index.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5w3JQkvVi?url=http://www.gamespot.com/gamespot/features/all/greatestgames/index.html |archivedate=2011-01-27 |work=GameSpot |accessdate=2006-05-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="nextgen">{{cite web|last=Campbell |first=Colin |date=2006-03-03 |title=Japan Votes on All Time Top 100 |url=http://www.next-gen.biz/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100 |work=Next Generation |accessdate=2006-05-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223200621/http://www.edge-online.com/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100 |archivedate=2012-02-23 }}</ref>。《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》第100期将游戏列入其“史上100佳任天堂游戏”的第8位<ref>{{cite journal |title=Nintendo Power's 100 Best Nintendo Games of All Time |journal=Nintendo Power |issue=100 |page=91 |date=September 1997}}</ref>，并在其20周年纪念刊上将其列为第五大超级任天堂游戏<ref name="np5best">{{Cite journal |journal=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]] |volume=231 |title=Best of the Best | pages= 73 | publisher=[[Future_US|Future US]]|date=August 2008}}</ref>。《穿越时空》也获评论者好评；GameSpot给游戏打了10分，是当时40,000个游戏中7个仅有的满分游戏之一，游戏还获得它们的2000年度游戏机游戏奖<ref name="perfect-10">{{cite web | date=2000-01-06 | first=Andrew | last=Vestal | title=GameSpot: Chrono Cross Review | url=http://www.gamespot.com/chrono-cross/reviews/2545933/chrono-cross-review | publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | accessdate=2006-07-24 | archive-date=2011-11-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111124192152/http://www.gamespot.com/chrono-cross/reviews/2545933/chrono-cross-review | dead-url=no }}</ref>。IGN给游戏打了9.7分，《穿越时空》还在他们2008年最佳100游戏榜单中名列第89<ref name="greatest-games4">{{cite web | year=2008 | title=IGN Top 100 Games 2008 | 89 Chrono Cross | url=http://top100.ign.com/2008/ign_top_game_89.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2009-03-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090224165621/http://top100.ign.com/2008/ign_top_game_89.html | archive-date=2009-02-24 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="ignreview">{{cite web | date=2000-08-15 | author=David Zdyrko | title=IGN: Chrono Cross Review | url=http://psx.ign.com/articles/162/162503p1.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2006-07-24 | archive-date=2006-08-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060810021705/http://psx.ign.com/articles/162/162503p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

系列音乐或高度评价并广为流行。IGN称《时空之轮》原声为“史上的最佳电子游戏原声音乐之一”，并称音乐是游戏能“俘获玩家情感”的一大环节。它还称原声为“RPG史上一些最难忘的旋律”<ref name="ign-review" />。游戏获得了《[[电子游戏月刊|电子游戏月刊]]》1995年电子游戏奖之“卡带游戏之最佳音乐奖”<ref name="egmbuyersguide1996">{{cite journal |year=1996 |month= |title=Electronic Gaming Monthly's Buyer's Guide |journal= Electronic Gaming Monthly |volume= |issue= |pages= |url=}}</ref>。《穿越时空》的原声获得2000年[[索尼|索尼]]PlayStation奖的金奖<ref name="mitsuda2008">{{cite web | last=Mitsuda | first=Yasunori | date=2008-01-28 | title=Radical Dreamer: Yasunori Mitsuda Interview from 1UP.com | url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=0&cId=3162780 | publisher=1UP.com | accessdate=2008-02-08 | archive-date=2012-12-05 | archive-url=https://archive.today/20121205003225/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=0&cId=3162780 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。IGN在游戏评论中称原声音乐“是绝妙的配乐”<!-- "does wonders in stirring the emotional strings of the players as they're playing through the game" --><ref name="ignreview" />。在一个日本RPG作曲家专栏中，IGN认为光田康典在十大杰出音乐家中，继[[植松伸夫|植松伸夫]]排名第二<ref>{{cite web|url=http://music.ign.com/articles/937/937683p5.html|title=IGN: Top Ten JRPG Composers|publisher=IGN|last=Sullivan|first=Meghan|date=2008-12-18|accessdate=2009-05-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/60wMrjrOM?url=http://music.ign.com/articles/937/937683p5.html|archivedate=2011-08-14}}</ref>。

